<h1 style=3D'margin:0in;font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:16.0pt;
color:#1E4E79'>流行病學</h1>

<ul type=3Ddisc style=3D'direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
 margin-bottom:0in'>
 <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
     style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt' lang=3Dzh-TW>自發性破裂（</span><span
     style=3D'font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt' lang=3Dzh-TW>Boerhaave syndrome</span><span
     style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt' lang=3Dzh-TW>）：男</span><span
     style=3D'font-family:Lato;font-size:12.0pt;color:#1A1C1C;background:white'
     lang=3Dzh-TW>&nbsp;&gt;</span><span style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";
     font-size:12.0pt;color:#1A1C1C;background:white' lang=3Den-US> 女</span><span
     style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt' lang=3Dzh-TW>（</span><span
     style=3D'font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt' lang=3Dzh-TW>3</span><span
     style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt' lang=3Dzh-TW>：</span><span
     style=3D'font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt' lang=3Dzh-TW>1</span><span
     style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt' lang=3Dzh-TW>）</span></li>
 <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
     style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>約三分之二的患者，穿孔局限於</span><span
     style=3D'font-weight:bold;font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>胸段食道（</span><span
     style=3D'font-weight:bold;font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt'>thoracic
     esophagus</span><span style=3D'font-weight:bold;font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";
     font-size:11.0pt'>）</span><span style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";
     font-size:11.0pt'>，剩下三分之一則涉及腹部食道</span></li>
</ul>

<h1 style=3D'margin:0in;font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:16.0pt;
color:#1E4E79'>病因</h1>

<ul type=3Ddisc style=3D'direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
 margin-bottom:0in'>
 <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
     style=3D'font-weight:bold;font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'
     lang=3Dzh-TW>自發性（</span><span style=3D'font-weight:bold;font-family:Calibri;
     font-size:11.0pt' lang=3Den-US>15%</span><span style=3D'font-weight:bold;
     font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt' lang=3Dzh-TW>）：</span><span
     style=3D'font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt' lang=3Dzh-TW>Boerhaave syndrome</span></li>
 <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
     style=3D'font-weight:bold;font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>醫源性</span></li>
 <ul type=3Ddisc style=3D'direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
  margin-bottom:0in'>
  <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
      style=3D'font-weight:bold;font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>最常見</span></li>
  <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
      style=3D'font-weight:bold;font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>上消化道內視鏡、手術</span></li>
 </ul>
 <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
     style=3D'font-weight:bold;font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'
     lang=3Dzh-TW>異物或腐蝕性物質（</span><span style=3D'font-weight:bold;font-family:Calibri;
     font-size:11.0pt' lang=3Den-US>14%</span><span style=3D'font-weight:bold;
     font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt' lang=3Dzh-TW>）</span></li>
 <ul type=3Ddisc style=3D'direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
  margin-bottom:0in'>
  <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
      style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>骨頭、假牙</span></li>
  <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
      style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>強鹼、強酸物質：清潔劑、電池</span></li>
 </ul>
 <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
     style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt' lang=3Dzh-TW>外傷（</span><span
     style=3D'font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt' lang=3Den-US>10%</span><span
     style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt' lang=3Dzh-TW>）</span></li>
 <ul type=3Ddisc style=3D'direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
  margin-bottom:0in'>
  <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
      style=3D'font-weight:bold;font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>鈍傷、穿刺傷</span></li>
 </ul>
 <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
     style=3D'font-weight:bold;font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>惡性腫瘤</span></li>
 <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
     style=3D'font-weight:bold;font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>感染</span></li>
 <ul type=3Ddisc style=3D'direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
  margin-bottom:0in'>
  <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
      style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>念珠菌（</span><span
      style=3D'font-weight:bold;font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt'>Candida
      spp.</span><span style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>）</span></li>
  <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
      style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>單純皰疹（</span><span
      style=3D'font-weight:bold;font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt'>Herpes
      simplex</span><span style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:
      11.0pt'>）</span></li>
  <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
      style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>結核（</span><span
      style=3D'font-weight:bold;font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt'>Tuberculosis</span><span
      style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>）</span></li>
  <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
      style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>梅毒（</span><span
      style=3D'font-weight:bold;font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt'>Syphilis</span><span
      style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>）</span></li>
 </ul>
</ul>

<h1 style=3D'margin:0in;font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:16.0pt;
color:#1E4E79'>病生理</h1>

<h1 style=3D'margin:0in;font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:16.0pt;
color:#1E4E79'>臨床特徵</h1>

<ul type=3Ddisc style=3D'direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
 margin-bottom:0in'>
 <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
     style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt' lang=3Dzh-TW>症狀通常不具特異性，所以對於近期有誘發因子（嘔吐、上消化道內視鏡、創傷、食道</span><span
     style=3D'font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt' lang=3Den-US>/</span><span
     style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt' lang=3Dzh-TW>縱膈腫瘤），需保持高度懷疑</span></li>
 <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
     style=3D'font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt'>Mackler triad</span></li>
 <ul type=3Ddisc style=3D'direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
  margin-bottom:0in'>
  <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
      style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>嘔吐</span></li>
  <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
      style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>胸骨後疼痛（</span><span
      style=3D'font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt'>retrosternal pain</span><span
      style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>）：劇烈、常放射至背部</span></li>
  <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
      style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>皮下或縱膈氣腫（</span><span
      style=3D'font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt'>Subcutaneous or mediastinal
      emphysema</span><span style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:
      11.0pt'>）</span></li>
  <ul type=3Ddisc style=3D'direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
   margin-bottom:0in'>
   <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
       style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>鎖骨上窩及頸部可聽到摩擦音（</span><span
       style=3D'font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt'>crepitus</span><span
       style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>）</span></li>
   <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
       style=3D'font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt' lang=3Den-US>Hamman Sign</span><span
       style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt' lang=3Dzh-TW>：胸部聽診時可聽見爆裂音（</span><span
       style=3D'font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt' lang=3Dzh-TW>crackling sound</span><span
       style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt' lang=3Dzh-TW>）</span></li>
  </ul>
 </ul>
 <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
     style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>疼痛：上腹、胸、頸部、喉嚨</span></li>
 <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
     style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>呼吸困難、心跳加快</span></li>
 <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
     style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>吞嚥困難</span></li>
 <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
     style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>病情惡化時，會演變成敗血症或多重器官衰竭</span></li>
 <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
     style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt' lang=3Dzh-TW>若近期內有進行內視鏡檢查，症狀通常在術後</span><span
     style=3D'font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt' lang=3Den-US> </span><span
     style=3D'font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt' lang=3Dzh-TW>24 </span><span
     style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt' lang=3Dzh-TW>小時內出現</span></li>
</ul>

<h1 style=3D'margin:0in;font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:16.0pt;
color:#1E4E79'>診斷</h1>

<ul type=3Ddisc style=3D'direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
 margin-bottom:0in'>
 <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
     style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt' lang=3Dzh-TW>頸部、胸部、腹部</span><span
     style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt' lang=3Den-US> </span><span
     style=3D'font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt' lang=3Dzh-TW>X </span><span
     style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt' lang=3Dzh-TW>光：初步診斷</span></li>
 <ul type=3Ddisc style=3D'direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
  margin-bottom:0in'>
  <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
      style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>縱膈擴大（</span><span
      style=3D'font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt'>Widened mediastinum</span><span
      style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>）</span></li>
  <ul type=3Ddisc style=3D'direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
   margin-bottom:0in'>
   <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
       style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>由水腫（</span><span
       style=3D'font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt'>edema</span><span
       style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>）</span><span
       style=3D'font-weight:bold;font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>引起，</span><span
       style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>可能需數小時後才會發生</span></li>
  </ul>
  <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
      style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>縱膈氣腫（</span><span
      style=3D'font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt'>Pneumomediastinum</span><span
      style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>）：穿孔的重要指標</span></li>
  <ul type=3Ddisc style=3D'direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
   margin-bottom:0in'>
   <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
       style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>通常需</span><span
       style=3D'font-weight:bold;font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>至少</span><span
       style=3D'font-weight:bold;font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt'>1</span><span
       style=3D'font-weight:bold;font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>小時</span><span
       style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>後才能在影像上顯現</span></li>
   <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
       style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>出現在約 </span><span
       style=3D'font-weight:bold;font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt'>40% </span><span
       style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>的患者中</span></li>
   <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
       style=3D'font-weight:bold;font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>胸段食道穿孔（</span><span
       style=3D'font-weight:bold;font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt'>thoracic
       perforation</span><span style=3D'font-weight:bold;font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";
       font-size:11.0pt'>）</span><span style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";
       font-size:11.0pt'>：縱膈氣腫</span></li>
  </ul>
  <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
      style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>氣胸</span></li>
  <ul type=3Ddisc style=3D'direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
   margin-bottom:0in'>
   <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
       style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt' lang=3Dzh-TW>若有肋膜破裂，</span><span
       style=3D'font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt' lang=3Den-US>77%</span><span
       style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt' lang=3Den-US>患者會出現氣胸</span></li>
   <ul type=3Ddisc style=3D'direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
    margin-bottom:0in'>
    <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
        style=3D'font-weight:bold;font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt'>2/3</span><span
        style=3D'font-weight:bold;font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:
        11.0pt'>：左側</span></li>
    <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
        style=3D'font-weight:bold;font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt'>1/5</span><span
        style=3D'font-weight:bold;font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:
        11.0pt'>：右側</span></li>
    <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
        style=3D'font-weight:bold;font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt'>1/10</span><span
        style=3D'font-weight:bold;font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:
        11.0pt'>：雙側</span></li>
   </ul>
  </ul>
  <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
      style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>氣腹（</span><span
      style=3D'font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt'>pneumoperitoneum</span><span
      style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>）、皮下氣腫（</span><span
      style=3D'font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt'>subcutaneous emphysema</span><span
      style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>）</span></li>
  <ul type=3Ddisc style=3D'direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
   margin-bottom:0in'>
   <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
       style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>皮下氣腫可靠側面頸部</span><span
       style=3D'font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt'> X </span><span
       style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>光發現</span></li>
  </ul>
 </ul>
</ul>

<p style=3D'margin:0in;margin-left:1.125in;font-size:11.0pt'><span
style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei"'>頸段食道穿孔（</span><span style=3D'font-family:
